926e3584-699d-4abf-9c1d-86178b6fbe34.60258f83-63c4-4bdd-8b64-aabe53baeeb6.description=This workflow updates the Process Instance State using PEM API. Inputs\: _PROCESS_INSTANCE_ID - Process Instance Id _processInstanceState - Process Instance State (Use value from selection list CSA-ProcessInstance-State) Result\: _processInstanceState -Updated Process Instance State 926e3584-699d-4abf-9c1d-86178b6fbe34.e9bd6d24-c15c-4f4f-ba46-522e6cd6000e.description=Generic flow to send an e-mail 926e3584-699d-4abf-9c1d-86178b6fbe34.f293ee61-93ed-4f18-8d4e-7536c1bcc261.description=This workflow returns the component properties and values using Artifact APIs. result\: propertyNameValuesList\: pipe separated list of property name and values ( where each property name and values would be ; seprated and multiple values would be , seprated) e.g. - property 1; value1,value2|property 2; value3|property 3; value3,value4|........ 926e3584-699d-4abf-9c1d-86178b6fbe34.f93e3792-9548-4821-af67-4ecdf17e8551.description=
This operation is used to retrieve a value from a list. When the index of an element from a list is known, this operation can be used to extract the element.

Inputs\:
    list - A list to get the value from.
    delimiter - The delimiter that separates values in the list.
Default value\: ','
    index - The index of the value (starting at 0) to retrieve from the list.
Valid values\: an integer, end (for the last element), end-1 (for the second to last element)

Results\:
    returnResult - This is the primary output. It contains the value found at the specified index in the list, if the value specified for the "index" input field is positive and less than the size of the list. Otherwise, it contains the value specified for "index".

Responses\:
     success - The operation completed as stated in the description.
     failure - The operation completed unsuccessfully.
